        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "2026 Canadian Improv Games | National Finals |  Sat, Apr 18, 2026, 7:30 pm | Babs Asper Theatre"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#image": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "https://naccnaca-eventimages.s3.amazonaws.com/40899/cig_cover_image__large.jpg"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Canada’s Brightest Young Stars. Infinite imagination. No script.\n\nWitness the grand finale of the 2026 Canadian Improv Games! After a week of intense competition, the top five high school teams from across the country take the stage at the National Arts Centre for one night of pure, unscripted magic. From heart-pounding drama to side-splitting comedy, these students create entire worlds based solely on your suggestions.\n\nCanada’s top 5 teams from the preliminary round will perform. The lineup will be determined the evening..."
      }
    ],
