      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Get on your feet and let’s get loud with the greatest hits of the ’90s and ’00s Latin pop explosion!  \n\nLa Vida Loca celebrates artists including Enrique Iglesias, Gloria Estefan, Santana, Ricky Martin, and more. Conductor Enrico Lopez-Yañez, vocalists Ender Thomas and Jackie Mendez, José Sibaja on trumpet, and Luisito Quintero on percussion join the NAC Orchestra for a high-octane program featuring all-new symphonic arrangements by Lopez-Yañez and Sibaja."
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns/fb#admins": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "728780803"
      }
    ],
