    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "An NAC English Theatre/Tarragon Theatre Co-production in association with fu-GEN Asian Theatre Company\nCo-commissioned by NAC English Theatre and NAC Orchestra \n\nWhat if your house had a mind of its own?\n\nIn 2032, while on the hunt for a new home in Toronto’s Trinity Bellwoods, Trim and Janie are drawn to a very peculiar house. A flood with no leak, an ominous voice, and hordes of cicadas are only three of the many strange things seeping up through the old floorboards. Could a strangely..."
      }
    ],
